"1501162P5-1.0-B Rev:1.0sp4" is silkscreened on the LCD controller board in the FCC photos. This device appears to be internally identical to the [[TP-LINK Touch P5]] except the USB ports and the WAN port are not populated. CPU1 and WI1/WI2 info are copied from the Touch P5 since the IDs are not visible in the FCC photos.
